55. Develop a PHP script that uses stack functions to reverse a string.
ANSWER
<?php
function reverseStringUsingStack($input) {
    // Step 1: Convert the string into an array of characters
    $chars = str_split($input);
   // Step 2: Push each character onto the stack
    $stack = [];
    foreach ($chars as $char) {
        array_push($stack, $char); // Push to stack
    }
  // Step 3: Pop each character off the stack to form the reversed string
    $reversed = '';
    while (!empty($stack)) {
        $reversed .= array_pop($stack); // Pop from stack
    }

    return $reversed;
}
// Example usage
$original = "OpenAI GPT-4";
$reversed = reverseStringUsingStack($original);
echo "Original String: $original\n";
echo "Reversed String: $reversed\n";
?>

OUTPUT
Original String: OpenAI GPT-4 Reversed String: 4-TPG IAnepO

